text: This is the parent for all Workflow events. The following fields are included: workflowKey - The name of the internal workflow key. workflowName - A list indicating what workflow(s) information to select. workflowGroupName - The name of the workflow group. The following fields are inherited from the Base event, and described in more detail in Base Event : category contents - Workflow: <Workflow name> eventName origin receiveTimeStamp severity timeStamp
title: Workflow Event - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
